text: It wasn't merely moral support that Sprouse offered his gal at the fashion show. He also showed up with a Shake Shack bag, just in case his model love got hungry off the runway."You know what, it's hard to see like from these interviews and I guess just from the Instagram posts and stuff how hard she's really worked to do this," Sprouse revealed to E! of Palvin's fashion show performance. "So I think the best part for me is just knowing that like after all of that, it really paid off. So I'm excited to see the coalescence of all that work."
